sudo pacman -S xorg picom 

$ cat /usr/share/xsessions/reiDwm.desktop
[Desktop Entry]
Encoding=UTF-8
Name=reiDWM
Comment=Dynamic Window Manager
Exec=startdwm
Icon=dwm
Type=XSession

$ cat /home/_ryu/.local/bin/startdwm
#!/bin/sh
picom &
exec dwm

Add /home/_ryu/.local/bin/startdwm to PATH in .zshrc or what-ever!

Clone a version of Dwm

make & make install!!


